title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Double Rewards on Auto Shop Client Jobs
content:
Get into a legitimate line of automotive work with Auto Shop Client Jobs and follow client specs or go off script to earn 2X GTA$ and LS Car Meet Rep — doubling up to 4X for GTA+ Members.

Deliver three vehicles to satisfy the Weekly Challenge and earn a GTA$100,000 bonus.

Visit the Maze Bank Foreclosures site to purchase an Auto Shop and equip it with Upgrades and Modifications — all for 40% off.
